Pagination can be implted with the <jw-pagination> component that comes 
with the jw-angular-pagination package which is available on npm.

step 1; install package and import it

Important Thing: It Reqyired two properties FOR using it.
Items : The array of items to be paged(It means how many item item
include in one page.)

changepage: call back function for handling change event

0--other Properties: 
***** pageSize: The items displayed on each page
 **** maxPages: The max number of page links to displayed
                in Navigation(Default to 10)
***** initial page: The initial page to be displayed